{{zh-hanzi|[[上]][[知]][[天文]]，[[下]][[知]][[地理]]}}
==Mandarin==
===Etymology===
Literally: Know the astronomy above, and know the geography below.

===Idiom===
{{PAGENAME}} (''[[Pinyin]]'' shàng zhī tiānwén, xià zhī dìlĭ)
# describes someone who is very learned; a [[polymath]]

